edBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:26:59.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割席<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n呢個係我地行到呢步既原因<br />\n我地要堅持落去"},{"pid":"d76dc0327a23fec6af871ed1d491f998ae744dfa","tid":1635533,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T23:53:21.000Z","msg":"高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e52f175fe7f3e5960283a266c811854b25393d","tid":1635533,"uid":196430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f304673fa5fb534aefb7337d82cec099c98d365","tid":1635533,"uid":46822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:04:39.000Z","msg":"點睇侵侵突然敍利亞撤兵 又搞一壇大野出黎<br />\n似乎彈劾案冇咁易完結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:39:08.000Z","msg":"集中資源對抗中共<br />\n<br />\n美國石油可以自給自足之後，中東價值已經好細，而且好煩同複雜<br />\n<br />\n之前伊朗刻意搞沙地，都係中共背後操縱想分散美國注意力嘅陷阱，第三次波斯灣戰爭爆發，當中要處理嘅嘢又會多好多，但美國政府雖然有能力開戰，但都決定忍手，今日更加當庫爾德人係condom撤兵，證明咗美國完全從中東抽身嘅決心，就係要集中資源搞中美關係"},{"pid":"618b451b3737e5d3602aa060064afd8a539a8645","tid":1635533,"uid":196430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f304673fa5fb534aefb7337d82cec099c98d365","tid":1635533,"uid":46822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:04:39.000Z","msg":"點睇侵侵突然敍利亞撤兵 又搞一壇大野出黎<br />\n似乎彈劾案冇咁易完結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:41:37.000Z","msg":"彈劾案應該會好似通俄門咁，得個嘈字，最後彈劾失敗侵侵咪又係贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f10b44513fc940090b213d6f534a08c9e2bf3d","tid":1635533,"uid":196430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a411ece099e7f995ecee957961c6c6f52be77dee","tid":1635533,"uid":202707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:09:15.000Z","msg":"NBA Morey單嘢應該都係美國其中一招"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:42:53.000Z","msg":"時機吻合到癲嘅完美風暴，話係巧合你信唔信？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1ea7fe7609